{EAST has a powerful hand, but 21 points is not strong enough to start with a forcing 2\C bid. 
Since he has balanced distribution he opens 2NT (20-21 points).

WEST adds her 6 points to EAST's minimum and concludes they should be in game. She expects her 
good \D suit to be useful to WEST in Notrump so she bids 3NT.}

